# Card Conventions

## Overview

Faru cards are markdown files in `backlog/`. The filesystem is the source of truth — the board is a view layer.

## Backlog Structure

```
backlog/
└── YYYY-MM-DD-TYPE-TITLE/
    ├── CARD.md                  # Primary card file (or *-milestones.md)
    ├── PREFIX-milestones.md     # Optional milestone definitions
    └── PREFIX-N-report.md         # Milestone completion reports
```

### Folder Naming

Format: `YYYY-MM-DD-TYPE-TITLE`

- `YYYY-MM-DD`: creation date
- `TYPE`: uppercase category (must match a `cardCategories` entry)
- `TITLE`: uppercase, hyphens instead of spaces

Example: `2026-04-20-PRODUCT-OAUTH-LOGIN`

## CARD.md Frontmatter

```yaml
---
title: Human-readable title
type: product          # lowercase, from cardCategories
status: todo           # todo | wip | done
assigned: alice
created: 2026-04-15
edited: 2026-04-15
description: One-line summary
links:
  - specs/oauth-design.md
---
```

| Field | Required | Notes |
|-------|----------|-------|
| `title` | yes | Display name |
| `type` | yes | Lowercase category from config |
| `status` | yes | `todo`, `wip`, or `done` — only three columns |
| `assigned` | yes | Git username |
| `created` | yes | ISO date |
| `edited` | yes | Update on every change |
| `description` | recommended | One-line summary for card tiles |
| `links` | optional | External references shown in sidebar |

## Primary File Resolution

Faru picks the primary file for frontmatter in this order:

1. `*-milestones.md`
2. `CARD.md`
3. `*-spec.md`
4. Any `.md` file

## Milestones

A `PREFIX-milestones.md` file defines milestones with `## PREFIX-N:` headings:

```yaml
---
title: My Project
type: infra
status: wip
assigned: alice
created: 2026-04-14
edited: 2026-04-14
description: Short summary
---

# VX Milestones

## VX-1: Research & Design

> Scope and acceptance criteria.

## VX-2: Implementation
```

A milestone is **done** when `PREFIX-N-report.md` exists in the same folder. The board shows progress like `● 2/3`.

## Comments

Comments are stored as a `## Comments` section in `CARD.md`. Added from the card detail view.

## Weekly Goal

`weekly-goal.md` in the project root holds a single line describing the current week's focus.

## Housekeeping

When completing milestone work:

1. Update milestone status in `*-milestones.md` — check off completed items.
2. Sync frontmatter `status` — if all milestones done, set `status: done`.
3. Update `edited` date in frontmatter to the current date.

## Anti-Patterns

1. **Extra status columns** — only todo, wip, done
2. **Cards outside `backlogDir`** — must live under configured backlog path
3. **Missing frontmatter** — board cannot render the card
4. **TYPE mismatch** — folder TYPE must match a configured `cardCategories` entry
